creditors in its appeal to join the group 
the committees goal is to recoup as much money as possible for 
more than 2000 creditors 
drexel still owes the sec 150 million of a 650 million 
settlement of securities fraud charges the unpaid amount would 
compensate individual investors who can prove they were harmed by 
drexels actions 
but the sec was left off the committee when it was formed last 
